<div>
	<p style="font-size: 14px;;">
		<b>Duroty System is the Gmail Open Source.<br> </b>
	</p>
	<p style="font-size: 14px;;">
		Duroty is a service of personal feeds, management of the mail, management of bookmarks and next will have also management of electronic agenda and indexing of files.
	</p>
	<p style="font-size: 14px;;">
		Duroty is oriented to small and medium companies that need information systems and management of the knowledge to diminish the barrier of access to the information.
	</p>
	<p style="font-size: 14px;;">
		It uses systems search of simple messages and outposts similar to the finder of webs Google, but with the possibility of looking for within the received attached files (Word, PowerPoint, excel, pdf, HTML, etc.) in addition to the typical fields (from,
		to, subject, body, etc.)
	</p>
	<p style="font-size: 14px;;">
		The interface of consultation of all the applications uses technology AJAX (combination of DHTML, CSS, Javascript, XML and languages of servant). In addition the interface appears initially with 3 languages (Català , Castellano and English) being easy the
		translation to other languages. The servant is developed completely in Java.
	</p>
	<p style="font-size: 14px;;">
		For more information he can consult the technical documentation <a href="http://www.duroty.com" target="_blank">HERE</a> or write to duroty@gmail.com. <span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 255);"></span>
	</p>
